---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Annual Report FY2058"
  description="Weyland-Yutani Corporation Annual Report for fiscal year 2058. Chairman's letter, financial summary, division performance, strategic priorities, and capital allocation overview."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center py-24">
        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          INVESTOR RELATIONS
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white mb-8 leading-none uppercase">
          ANNUAL <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">REPORT</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-64 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-8"></div>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          FISCAL YEAR 2058 &mdash; A RECORD YEAR OF GROWTH, INNOVATION, AND SHAREHOLDER VALUE CREATION.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- CHAIRMAN'S LETTER -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">FROM THE CHAIRMAN AND CEO</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            LETTER TO <span class="text-[#FFC600]">SHAREHOLDERS</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="corp-card p-8 md:p-12">
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
            DEAR SHAREHOLDERS,
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
            FISCAL YEAR 2058 WAS A TRANSFORMATIVE YEAR FOR WEYLAND-YUTANI CORPORATION. WE DELIVERED RECORD REVENUE OF $45.2 TRILLION, AN 8.3% INCREASE OVER THE PRIOR YEAR, WHILE EXPANDING NET INCOME MARGINS TO 26.8%. THESE RESULTS REFLECT THE STRENGTH OF OUR DIVERSIFIED BUSINESS MODEL AND THE EXCEPTIONAL EXECUTION OF OUR TEAMS ACROSS ALL SEVEN OPERATING DIVISIONS.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
            OUR TERRAFORMING OPERATIONS DIVISION ACHIEVED A SIGNIFICANT MILESTONE, SURPASSING $8 TRILLION IN ANNUAL REVENUE FOR THE FIRST TIME AS WE BROUGHT 47 NEW ATMOSPHERIC PROCESSING INSTALLATIONS ONLINE. THE CYBERNETICS DIVISION LAUNCHED THE DAVID-9 SERIES, OUR MOST ADVANCED SYNTHETIC PLATFORM TO DATE, TO STRONG COMMERCIAL AND INSTITUTIONAL DEMAND.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
            IN ENERGY SYSTEMS, OUR NEXT-GENERATION FUSION REACTOR ACHIEVED COMMERCIAL VIABILITY, OPENING A NEW REVENUE STREAM ESTIMATED AT $3 TRILLION ANNUALLY AT FULL DEPLOYMENT. HEALTH SCIENCES CONTINUED ITS RAPID GROWTH WITH THE MEDPOD 5000 RECEIVING REGULATORY APPROVAL IN 42 JURISDICTIONS, BRINGING OUR AUTONOMOUS SURGICAL TECHNOLOGY TO BILLIONS MORE PATIENTS.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
            WE ALSO MADE STRATEGIC INVESTMENTS IN OUR FUTURE, ALLOCATING $6.8 TRILLION TO RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT, REPRESENTING 15% OF REVENUE. THIS INVESTMENT SUPPORTS OVER 200 ACTIVE R&D PROGRAMS SPANNING FTL PROPULSION OPTIMIZATION, ADVANCED MATERIALS, SYNTHETIC COGNITION, AND NEXT-GENERATION ATMOSPHERIC PROCESSING TECHNOLOGY.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
            OUR COMMITMENT TO RESPONSIBLE OPERATIONS REMAINED STEADFAST. WE INVESTED $1.2 TRILLION IN SUSTAINABILITY INITIATIVES, EXPANDED THE EXPLORERS ACADEMY TO 250,000 STUDENTS, AND MAINTAINED OUR POSITION AS THE LEADING EMPLOYER OF MILITARY VETERANS WORLDWIDE.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
            LOOKING AHEAD, I AM CONFIDENT IN OUR STRATEGIC POSITION. THE DEMAND FOR TERRAFORMING, ENERGY, AND HEALTHCARE SERVICES CONTINUES TO ACCELERATE AS HUMANITY EXPANDS ACROSS THE STARS. WEYLAND-YUTANI IS UNIQUELY POSITIONED TO MEET THAT DEMAND.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
            ON BEHALF OF THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS AND OUR 527,000 EMPLOYEES, THANK YOU FOR YOUR CONTINUED TRUST AND INVESTMENT IN OUR COMPANY.
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-[#1a1a1a] pt-6 mt-8">
            <div class="text-white font-black text-sm uppercase">HIDEO YUTANI III</div>
            <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs uppercase">CHAIRMAN AND CHIEF EXECUTIVE OFFICER</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FINANCIAL SUMMARY -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">FINANCIAL PERFORMANCE</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            KEY <span class="text-[#FFC600]">METRICS</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8 md:p-12">
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center border-b border-[#FFC600]/30 pb-4">
                <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs uppercase">METRIC</div>
                <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs uppercase">FY2058</div>
                <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs uppercase">FY2057</div>
                <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs uppercase">CHANGE</div>
              </div>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">
                <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase text-left">REVENUE</div>
                <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm">$45.2T</div>
                <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm">$41.7T</div>
                <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm">+8.3%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">
                <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase text-left">NET INCOME</div>
                <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm">$12.1T</div>
                <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm">$10.4T</div>
                <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm">+16.3%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">
                <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase text-left">EPS</div>
                <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm">$238.41</div>
                <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm">$204.88</div>
                <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm">+16.4%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">
                <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase text-left">FREE CASH FLOW</div>
                <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm">$9.8T</div>
                <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm">$8.3T</div>
                <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm">+18.1%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">
                <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase text-left">DIVIDENDS PAID</div>
                <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm">$6.9T</div>
                <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm">$6.2T</div>
                <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm">+11.3%</div>
              </div>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center">
                <div class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase text-left">R&D SPEND</div>
                <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm">$6.8T</div>
                <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm">$5.9T</div>
                <div class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm">+15.3%</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- DIVISION PERFORMANCE -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">SEGMENT REPORTING</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            DIVISION <span class="text-[#FFC600]">PERFORMANCE</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">TERRAFORMING OPERATIONS</h3>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">$8.2T</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mb-4">REVENUE &bull; +11.4% YOY</div>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">47 NEW ATP INSTALLATIONS. 12 ATMOSPHERES DECLARED BREATHABLE. RECORD BACKLOG OF $24T IN CONTRACTED PROJECTS.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">CYBERNETICS & SYNTHETICS</h3>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">$7.1T</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mb-4">REVENUE &bull; +9.2% YOY</div>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">DAVID-9 SERIES LAUNCH. 15,000 UNITS DELIVERED. AUTONOMOUS SYSTEMS DIVISION GREW 22% ON INDUSTRIAL DEMAND.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">ENERGY SYSTEMS</h3>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">$6.8T</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mb-4">REVENUE &bull; +7.6% YOY</div>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">NEXT-GEN FUSION REACTOR COMMERCIALIZED. FTL DRIVE EFFICIENCY IMPROVED 12%. 30 NEW POWER INSTALLATIONS COMPLETED.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">SECURITY SOLUTIONS</h3>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">$6.4T</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mb-4">REVENUE &bull; +5.8% YOY</div>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">EXPANDED GOVERNMENT CONTRACTS. NEW PERIMETER DEFENSE SYSTEMS FOR 85 COLONIES. CYBERSECURITY DIVISION GREW 18%.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">HEALTH SCIENCES</h3>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">$5.9T</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mb-4">REVENUE &bull; +14.2% YOY</div>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">MEDPOD 5000 APPROVED IN 42 JURISDICTIONS. PHARMACEUTICAL DIVISION SECURED 12 NEW PATENTS. COLONY HEALTHCARE CONTRACTS EXPANDED.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-2 uppercase">ELECTRONICS & BIOLOGICAL SCIENCES</h3>
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">$10.8T</div>
            <div class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mb-4">COMBINED REVENUE &bull; +6.1% YOY</div>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">HOLOGRAPHIC SYSTEMS ADOPTED BY 200+ COMMERCIAL CLIENTS. BIOLOGICAL RESEARCH DELIVERED 8 NEW COMMERCIAL APPLICATIONS.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STRATEGIC PRIORITIES -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">LOOKING AHEAD</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            STRATEGIC <span class="text-[#FFC600]">PRIORITIES</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-3 uppercase">1. ACCELERATE TERRAFORMING CAPACITY</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">INCREASE ATMOSPHERIC PROCESSOR PRODUCTION BY 30% OVER THE NEXT THREE YEARS TO MEET SURGING DEMAND FROM THE COLONIAL ADMINISTRATION AND PRIVATE COLONIZATION ENTITIES. INVEST $4T IN NEW MANUFACTURING FACILITIES ON EARTH AND LUNA.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-3 uppercase">2. EXPAND HEALTH SCIENCES GLOBALLY</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">DEPLOY MEDPOD TECHNOLOGY TO ALL COLONY WORLDS AND EXPAND EARTH-SIDE DISTRIBUTION TO UNDERSERVED MARKETS. TARGET: 500,000 MEDPOD INSTALLATIONS BY FY2062, MAKING AUTONOMOUS SURGICAL CARE UNIVERSALLY ACCESSIBLE.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-3 uppercase">3. ADVANCE SYNTHETIC INTELLIGENCE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">CONTINUE INVESTMENT IN THE DAVID SERIES PLATFORM WITH A FOCUS ON COGNITIVE ENHANCEMENT AND SPECIALIZED APPLICATIONS. EXPAND THE SYNTHETIC WORKFORCE TO SUPPORT HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS AND ACCELERATE COLONY DEVELOPMENT.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-3 uppercase">4. DISCIPLINED CAPITAL RETURN</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">MAINTAIN OUR COMMITMENT TO RETURNING CAPITAL TO SHAREHOLDERS THROUGH DIVIDENDS AND SHARE REPURCHASES. THE BOARD HAS AUTHORIZED A NEW $2T BUYBACK PROGRAM AND APPROVED A 10% INCREASE IN THE QUARTERLY DIVIDEND.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- RISK FACTORS -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">DISCLOSURE</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            RISK <span class="text-[#FFC600]">FACTORS</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="corp-card p-8 md:p-12">
          <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
            INVESTORS SHOULD CAREFULLY CONSIDER THE FOLLOWING RISK FACTORS, AMONG OTHERS, WHEN EVALUATING AN INVESTMENT IN WEYLAND-YUTANI CORPORATION SECURITIES:
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">MARKET AND ECONOMIC RISK:</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase"> GLOBAL AND INTERSTELLAR ECONOMIC CONDITIONS MAY ADVERSELY AFFECT DEMAND FOR OUR PRODUCTS AND SERVICES. FLUCTUATIONS IN COMMODITY PRICES, CURRENCY EXCHANGE RATES, AND INTERSTELLAR TRADE POLICIES COULD IMPACT FINANCIAL RESULTS.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">REGULATORY RISK:</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase"> OUR OPERATIONS ARE SUBJECT TO EXTENSIVE REGULATION BY EARTH GOVERNMENTS, THE COLONIAL ADMINISTRATION, AND VARIOUS INTERNATIONAL BODIES. CHANGES IN REGULATION COULD INCREASE COMPLIANCE COSTS OR RESTRICT BUSINESS ACTIVITIES.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">OPERATIONAL RISK:</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase"> OFF-WORLD OPERATIONS INVOLVE INHERENT RISKS INCLUDING EQUIPMENT FAILURE, ENVIRONMENTAL HAZARDS, SUPPLY CHAIN DISRUPTION, AND PERSONNEL SAFETY CHALLENGES. CATASTROPHIC EVENTS COULD RESULT IN SIGNIFICANT FINANCIAL LOSSES.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">TECHNOLOGY RISK:</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase"> OUR COMPETITIVE POSITION DEPENDS ON CONTINUED INNOVATION. FAILURE TO DEVELOP NEW TECHNOLOGIES OR THE EMERGENCE OF DISRUPTIVE COMPETITORS COULD ADVERSELY AFFECT MARKET SHARE AND PROFITABILITY.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase">GEOPOLITICAL RISK:</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase"> POLITICAL INSTABILITY ON EARTH OR IN COLONIAL TERRITORIES COULD DISRUPT OPERATIONS, DAMAGE ASSETS, OR RESTRICT MARKET ACCESS. INTERGOVERNMENTAL DISPUTES MAY AFFECT TRADE AND BUSINESS CONDITIONS.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mt-6">
            THIS IS NOT AN EXHAUSTIVE LIST OF RISK FACTORS. PLEASE REFER TO OUR ANNUAL REPORT ON FORM 10-K FILED WITH THE SECURITIES AND EXCHANGE COMMISSION FOR A COMPLETE DISCUSSION OF RISKS AND UNCERTAINTIES.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
